{"tid":1404750,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想整針對旅客外文文宣的巴絲, 同我入來!","createTime":"2019-08-04T05:53:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T05:53:29.000Z","uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"da936b175f9c2a0a276aa0eb1c3f6d864e1e6b0f","tid":1404750,"uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:53:29.000Z","msg":"近年訪港旅客排名<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tourism_in_Hong_Kong#Top_15_most_visiting_nationalities\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FTourism_in_Hong_Kong%23Top_15_most_visiting_nationalities&d=Yc7MVk%2FjSym3Ma7OIK9USJ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=c0304ebe\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tourism_in_Hong_Kong#Top_15_most_visiting_nationalities</a><br />\n<br />\n要效用最大, <br />\n就要針對頭15名的地區<br />\n其中大陸佔比最多(~80%), 台灣(2.5%)次之, 南韓日本再次之.<br />\n<br />\n如果想要針對<span style=\"color: red;\">旅客</span>, 準備<span style=\"color: red;\">中英文以外</span>的文宣, <br />\n最有效的是韓文, 日文, 菲律賓話, 泰文, 印尼文.<br />\n留意韓國,日本都是勢力強大的G20國家, 而後三者都是外傭的祖國.<br />\n其次係印度文, 法文, 俄文 - 都是G20的國家."}]}